title: No Time to Die
plot: Bond has left active service and is enjoying a tranquil life in Jamaica. His peace is short-lived when his old friend Felix Leiter from the CIA turns up asking for help. The mission to rescue a kidnapped scientist turns out to be far more treacherous than expected, leading Bond onto the trail of a mysterious villain armed with dangerous new technology.
writers: Neal Purvis, Robert Wade, Cary Joji Fukunaga, Phoebe Waller-Bridge, Ian Fleming
stars: Daniel Craig, Ana de Armas, Rami Malek, Ralph Fiennes

similars.title: Spectre
similars.plot: A cryptic message from James Bond's past sends him on a trail to uncover the existence of a sinister organisation named SPECTRE. With a new threat dawning, Bond learns the terrible truth about the author of all his pain in his most recent missions.
similars.stars: Daniel Craig, Christoph Waltz, Léa Seydoux

similars.title: Skyfall
similars.plot: James Bond's loyalty to M is tested when her past comes back to haunt her. When MI6 comes under attack, 007 must track down and destroy the threat, no matter how personal the cost.
similars.stars: Daniel Craig, Javier Bardem, Naomie Harris

similars.title: Casino Royale
similars.plot: After earning 00 status and a licence to kill, Secret Agent James Bond sets out on his first mission as 007. Bond must defeat a private banker funding terrorists in a high-stakes game of poker at Casino Royale, Montenegro.
similars.stars: Daniel Craig, Eva Green, Judi Dench

similars.title: Quantum of Solace
similars.plot: James Bond descends into mystery as he tries to stop a mysterious organisation from eliminating a country's most valuable resource.
similars.stars: Daniel Craig, Olga Kurylenko, Mathieu Amalric

similars.title: Top Gun: Maverick
similars.plot: After more than thirty years of service as one of the Navy's top aviators, Pete Mitchell is where he belongs, pushing the envelope as a courageous test pilot and dodging the advancement in rank that would ground him.
similars.stars: Tom Cruise, Jennifer Connelly, Miles Teller

similars.title: The King's Man
similars.plot: In the early years of the 20th century, the Kingsman agency is formed to stand against a cabal plotting a war to wipe out millions.
similars.stars: Ralph Fiennes, Harris Dickinson, Gemma Arterton

similars.title: Dune
similars.plot: Feature adaptation of Frank Herbert's science fiction novel, about the son of a noble family entrusted with the protection of the most valuable asset and most vital element in the galaxy.

similars.title: Daniel Craig vs James Bond
similars.plot: Starting with a high-speed taxi sequence, Daniel is constantly recognized as James Bond by surprised locals as he hunts down his missing passport.

similars.title: Knives Out 2
similars.plot: Plot unknown. Sequel to the 2019 film 'Knives Out'.
similars.stars: Dave Bautista, Kathryn Hahn, Daniel Craig

similars.title: Jungle Cruise
similars.plot: Based on Disneyland's theme park ride where a small riverboat takes a group of travelers through a jungle filled with dangerous animals and reptiles but with a supernatural element.
similars.stars: Dwayne Johnson, Emily Blunt, Edgar Ramírez

similars.title: Purity
similars.plot: A young woman joins an activist group, and begins a global journey in search of her father.
